description:
Join us for this weeks Kardashian Recap

The Kardashians Season 1 Episode 2- Did somebody tape that?

Kim is rehearsing for SNL hosting debut, her past sex tape continues to haunt her, Khloe deals with ongoing anxiety, and Kourtney and Travis need to calm it down with the PDA!

If you want to see our live reactions, check out our YouTube video.
